readable.content: A black dog runs paralell to a wire fence in a grassy medow . A brown dog is running along a grassy stretch divided by strings . A dog runs past an empty chair and a tripod , between stretched strings , marking a path through a grassy field . A dog with all fours up in the air above the clover-filled grass . The gray dog is running on a green field .
